fields.name: Args
fields.description: Arguments to the entrypoint. The docker image's CMD is used if this is not provided.

fields.name: Command
fields.description: Entrypoint array. Not executed within a shell. The docker image's ENTRYPOINT is used if this is not provided.

fields.name: ContainerImage
fields.description: Container image of the custom container. This should be in the form of <repository>:<tag> without the server name of the registry

fields.name: LanguageFramework
fields.description: Language framework of the container image uploaded. Supported values: "springboot", "", null.

fields.name: Server
fields.description: The name of the registry that contains the container image
